summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5013 for the improvement of the alley between blocks 1 and 2, Star Addition and blocks 1 and 2, Hagan's Extension to Star Addition, being the alley from West Halladay Street to West Wheeler Street, between 7th Avenue West and 8th Avenue West; by paving and otherwise improving the same.
